    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This page is give an overview of the Relation between SUM_SSC and SUM_SSM"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Tx Protected message"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SUM_SSC is building and sending protected messages. However the calculation of the protected elements (ARC, PV, CS and CRC) is done by SUM_SSM"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "\"ARC” if only an ARC is used “ARC_PV” if an ARC and a PV are used “ARC_CS” if an ARC and a CS are used “ARC_CRC” if an ARC and a CRC are used"
    },
